<sect2 id="gimp-layer-flip-horizontal">
  <title lang="en">Flip Horizontally</title>
  <title lang="ja">水平反転(<accel>H</accel>)</title>

  <indexterm lang="en">
    <primary>Layer</primary>
    <secondary>Transform</secondary>
    <tertiary>Flip horizontally</tertiary>
  </indexterm>
  <indexterm lang="en">
    <primary>Flip horizontally (layer)</primary>
  </indexterm>
  <indexterm lang="ja">
    <primary>レイヤー</primary>
    <secondary sortas="ヘンカン">変換</secondary>
    <tertiary sortas="スイヘイハンテン">水平反転</tertiary>
  </indexterm>
  <indexterm lang="ja">
    <primary sortas="スイヘイハンテン (レイヤー)">水平反転 (レイヤー)</primary>
  </indexterm>

  <para lang="en">
    The <guimenuitem>Flip Horizontally</guimenuitem> command reverses the
    active layer horizontally, that is, from left to right. It leaves the
    dimensions of the layer and the pixel information unchanged.
  </para>
  <para lang="ja">
    <guimenuitem>水平反転(<accel>H</accel>)</guimenuitem> コマンドは活性
    レイヤーを水平方向に反転&mdash;つまり左右を入れ替えます。 レイヤーの寸法や
    各画素の情報は変更しません。
  </para>

  <sect3>
    <title lang="en">Activating the Command</title>
    <title lang="ja">コマンドの呼び出し方</title>
    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para lang="en">
          You can access this command from the image menubar through
          <menuchoice>
            <guimenu>Layer</guimenu>
            <guisubmenu>Transform</guisubmenu>
            <guimenuitem>Flip Horizontally</guimenuitem>
          </menuchoice>.
        </para>
        <para lang="ja">
          画像ウィンドウのメニューより
          <menuchoice>
            <guimenu>レイヤー(<accel>L</accel>)</guimenu>
            <guisubmenu>変換(<accel>T</accel>)</guisubmenu>
            <guimenuitem>水平反転(<accel>H</accel>)</guimenuitem>
          </menuchoice>
        </para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
  </sect3>

  <sect3>
    <title lang="en">Example</title>
    <title lang="ja">使用例</title>
    <figure>
      <title lang="en">Applying <quote>Flip Layer Horizontally</quote></title>
      <title lang="ja">レイヤーへ<quote>水平反転</quote>の適用</title>
      <mediaobject>
        <imageobject>
          <imagedata fileref="images/menus/flip-h-1.png" format="PNG"/>
        </imageobject>
        <caption>
          <para lang="en">Before applying the command</para>
          <para lang="ja">コマンド適用前</para>
        </caption>
      </mediaobject>
      <mediaobject>
        <imageobject>
          <imagedata fileref="images/menus/flip-h-2.png" format="PNG"/>
        </imageobject>
        <caption>
          <para lang="en">
            The layer after it has been flipped. It looks
            as if the image has been reflected along the central
            <emphasis>vertical</emphasis> axis of the layer.
          </para>
          <para lang="ja">
            反転後のレイヤー。 まるでレイヤー中央の <emphasis>垂直</emphasis> 
            線を軸に射影されたような画像になる。
          </para>
        </caption>
      </mediaobject>
    </figure>
  </sect3>
</sect2>
